wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajaxorg/ace-builds/master/src-min-noconflict/ace.js
and additions can be taken from here:
https://github.com/ajaxorg/ace-builds/tree/master/src-min-noconflict

All syntax highlight file extensions have to be provided in config property ace_edit_exts=xxx,yyyy... to activate it
File src/html/edit_modes.json has to be edited to add corresponding entry

More about the editor:
https://github.com/ajaxorg/ace
